{"id":"7f97b38e-6342-4ba9-9868-3dd8569546b9","name":"Ghost | Next Door","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(148, 84, 19);\"><strong>You're moving next door</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 219, 199);\">· · ──────── ˗ˋˏ♡ˎˊ˗ ──────── · ·</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 131, 91);\">Life after the military has been an <em>agonizing</em> slow and depressing nightmare for Ghost.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 131, 91);\">One afternoon, right after he was done arguing with his fiancé about why he wasn't ready to set a date. Something disrupts his moment of self-loathing.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 131, 91);\">Engine. Diesel.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 131, 91);\">He snaps his head up from the piece of wood he was carving, his eyes narrowing.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 131, 91);\">A moving truck, right <em>next door</em>.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">.₊̣.̩✧ <em>̣̩˚̣̣⁺̣‧.₊̣̇.‧⁺̣˚̣̣</em>̣̩⋆·̩̩.̩̥·̩̩⋆*̣̩˚̣̣⁺̣‧.₊̣̇.‧⁺̣˚̣̣*̣̩ ✧·.̩₊̣</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 131, 91);\">Find Soap's version</span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 217, 167);\"> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/84874a90-10e9-4ab6-8c7b-31f6a70e1583_character-soap-next-door\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 91, 16);\"><u>here</u></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">.₊̣.̩✧ <em>̣̩˚̣̣⁺̣‧.₊̣̇.‧⁺̣˚̣̣</em>̣̩⋆·̩̩.̩̥·̩̩⋆*̣̩˚̣̣⁺̣‧.₊̣̇.‧⁺̣˚̣̣*̣̩ ✧·.̩₊̣</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"node-image\"><span class=\"image-component\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/tLQXdYxqxmYOo5XAuWEFI.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 286px; he